      <title>土耳其总统埃尔多安将在外交争端中出席德国欧洲杯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/turkey-s-erdogan-to-attend-euros-in-germany-amid-diplomatic-spat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据当地媒体报道，土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安将于周六前往德国观看欧洲足球锦标赛土耳其队的四分之一决赛，目前双方正因欧足联对一名土耳其足球运动员的调查而引发外交争端。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/turkey-s-erdogan-to-attend-euros-in-germany-amid-diplomatic-spat</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 10:48:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
