      <title>政界领袖警告混乱，勒庞竞争对手势头强劲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/le-pen-s-rivals-gain-momentum-as-political-leaders-warn-of-chaos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在周日的立法选举之前，各政党为阻止玛丽娜·勒庞的极右翼国民联盟执政而做出的最后一搏获得了动力，关键的政治人物警告选民，他们的决定将极大地改变法国，并可能导致混乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/le-pen-s-rivals-gain-momentum-as-political-leaders-warn-of-chaos</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 08:18:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普雷特称欧洲央行必须为援助法国设定“非常高”的标准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/ecb-must-set-very-high-bar-for-any-help-to-france-praet-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行前首席经济学家彼得·普雷特 (Peter Praet) 表示，欧洲央行必须引导投资者，一旦金融市场出现压力，政策制定者不会轻易出手救助法国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/ecb-must-set-very-high-bar-for-any-help-to-france-praet-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 07:44:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
